        "body": "<p>I found out that it was a Button array from <code>javafx.scene.control.Button<\/code> in my <code>Event<\/code> class that was causing the problem. I fixed it by making it <code>transient<\/code> so it would get ignored by GSON and not cause any problems.<\/p>\n\n<p>Nevertheless, I have no idea why the Button array would cause this exception. Any thoughts?<\/p>\n",
